The teen was walking to school on Thursday morning when the accident happened. JOHANNESBURG A 14-year-old girl has died after she was hit by a train at a railway station in Ballito in KwaZulu-Natal.The teen was walking to school on Thursday morning when the accident happened. When paramedics arrived on the scene she was still in a critical condition.Netcare 911's Athlenda Mathe says, &quot;The girl was stabilised on scene and thereafter transported to a nearby hospital. Sadly, the girl succumbed to her injuries at the hospital s trauma unit. (Edited by Neo Koza)